8#ifndef SRC_TAG_PARSER_H_
9#define SRC_TAG_PARSER_H_
10
11#include "src/master_value_parser.h"
12#include "src/simple_tag_parser.h"
13#include "src/targets_parser.h"
14#include "webm/dom_types.h"
15#include "webm/id.h"
16
17namespace webm {
18
19// Spec reference:
20// http://matroska.org/technical/specs/index.html#Tag
21// http://www.webmproject.org/docs/container/#Tag
22class TagParser : public MasterValueParser<Tag> {
23 public:
24 TagParser()
25 : MasterValueParser<Tag>(
26 MakeChild<TargetsParser>(Id::kTargets, &Tag::targets),
27 MakeChild<SimpleTagParser>(Id::kSimpleTag, &Tag::tags)) {}
28
29 protected:
30 Status OnParseCompleted(Callback* callback) override {
31 return callback->OnTag(metadata(Id::kTag), value());
32 }
33};
34
35} // namespace webm
36
37#endif // SRC_TAG_PARSER_H_
